===================================================
            README
===================================================
1. Choose a secret key (a phrase)

2. Generate a public key:
   $ ./pegwit -i < my.sec > my.pub

   NOTE: The file my.sec containing a secret key is in plain ASCII format.

3. Encrypt a file:
   $ ./pegwit -e my.pub pgptest.plain pegwit.enc < encryption_junk

4. Decrypt a file:
   $ ./pegwit -d pegwit.enc pegwit.dec < my.sec

